dct_description_sm: From British and United States surveys to 1882 ; published June, 1883 at the Hydrographic Office under the authority of the Secretary of the Navy.
Depths shown by soundings, relief by hachures and spot heights.
Shows coastal relief, waterways, low water areas, various place names, islands, lights, railways.
dct_spatial_sm: Juan de Fuca, Strait of (B.C. and Wash.)
